description: Application for the approval of Reserved Matters for 253 residential units and 882.81sqm GIA community floorspace and nursery (D1) including ancillary café (D1/A3) with associated car parking, hard and soft landscaping, public realm, play space, streetscape and associated works pursuant to conditions LSC0.27 and LSC0.28 of the Legacy Communities Scheme outline planning permission 11/90621/OUTODA as varied by 14/00036/VAR being details of layout, scale, appearance, access and landscaping.
